After 10+ years in the construction industry, I have established a new renovation company in Ottawa.  With the main focus on bathroom, basement, and kitchen renovations; Pine Ridge Renovations is now open to new clients looking for high-quality, and reliable service. Call us today for free estimates for your project.

Phone: 343-262-1428
Email: Pineridgerenovations@gmail.com

Other services include:
Framing
Drywall installation & finishing
Trim work
Painting
Door & window installation
Siding
General repairs
